{"tid":1400282,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"你班冷氣軍師！同我po撤退路線！","createTime":"2019-08-03T12:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T12:26:54.000Z","uid":45788,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"50e426490cfd2cec9120565d39f5bd834e194af7","tid":1400282,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n禁錯,開過<br />\n第一次做，未必做得好好，有錯唔該即刻diu<br />\n紅色為示威者現場位置<br />\n黑色是黑社會預計清場位置<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwLzww2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwLzww2.png&h=c33933bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀要走主要有幾個方法:<br />\n1.搭船<br />\n2.圖片顯示<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WY1nFqo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWY1nFqo.png&h=14633531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA1:漆咸道南直上去,途中可以上poly U，唔上就可以行前，有條隧道去女童軍<br />\n行女童軍方向可以源球場去旺角，或者前往伊院方向去佐敦<br />\n行反方向就行到去hung hom,落隧道，途中可以入到polyu,唔入的話繼續的話可以行到曲街<br />\nA2:經漆咸道南，入去麼地道富豪酒店，行到水池個邊有橋去紅磡火車站，係個邊散(但有機會有狗)但可以轉入polyu,然後走A1路線<br />\nA3:跟星光大道，海邊行，可以行到黃埔碼頭(一條路)<br />\n<br />\n如果黑社會清場係咁的話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fxf7Rw4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffxf7Rw4.png&h=5251e529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA1:FAIL<br />\nA2:提防有狗，留意可以係天橋轉入Polyu再走A1路線<br />\nA3:照常<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n希望附近居民可以幫手的話快D入黎幫手<br />\nbe water"},{"pid":"6d2743f0e5953814d3017a1971360fcf77a766eb","tid":1400282,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fa4f1359e7fa8512bcd85a1cef3043b7fc3424","tid":1400282,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB